data.description: Welcome to 153 Sawgrass Drive, where luxurious living meets picturesque surroundings! This stunning three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home is a masterpiece of design, boasting exquisite features and a prime location within the prestigious Blue Bell Country Club. Situated in a neighborhood known for its upscale ambiance and breathtaking scenery, this home offers a lifestyle of unparalleled elegance and convenience.  Approaching the home, you'll be greeted by vibrant gardens, mature foliage, and lush greenery, all framing a picturesque waterfront view. Step inside a grand two-story foyer flooded with natural light and adorned with hardwood flooring. To the left, discover the bright and airy living room featuring a cathedral ceiling, hardwood flooring, and discerning chair railing. Through the rear pocket doors, find a private office with an ultra-high ceiling, oversized windows, and remote-powered blinds, offering tranquil waterfront views and direct access to the expansive rear deck.  Entering from the foyer, the formal dining room awaits, detailed with luxurious chair railing and crown molding, perfect for hosting dinner parties with friends and family. The gourmet chef’s kitchen is equipped with glistening white quartz countertops, a large center island with barstool seating, tasteful backsplash tiling, and plenty of wooden cabinetry with underlighting in the lower level and rear lighting in the upper-level cabinetry. The adjacent breakfast room, bathed in sunlight from skylights above, opens to the fenced-in sunken patio, blending indoor and outdoor living seamlessly. The impressive family room showcases a prominent, decorative stone surround gas fireplace complemented by hardwood flooring and a butler's pantry with a wine fridge for exquisite beverage service. Completing the first floor is a half-bathroom and a nice sized laundry room featuring gleaming white wooden cabinets and shelving for ample storage and convenience.  Ascending to the upper level, the primary suite exudes opulence with plush carpeting, skylights that bathe the space in natural light, and studio lighting to accentuate its grandeur. The renovated California-style walk-in closet is a masterpiece, boasting abundant custom shelving, storage solutions, and a spacious changing area, elevating the suite to the epitome of luxury living. Indulge in the spa-like ensuite bathroom, boasting a luxurious quartz-topped dual vanity, a glass-enclosed stall shower, and the convenience of a laundry chute, ensuring a truly elevated experience. Two more bedrooms with generous closet space and plush carpeting round out this level, with both sharing a full hall bathroom.  The substantial fully finished lower level of this remarkable property provides an expansive and versatile space, ideal for creating a luxurious second living area, and a private gym, additionally offering abundant storage options. The versatile additional bonus room in the basement featuring a large walk-in closet affords flexibility to your specific needs.    Step outside to the rear deck and immerse yourself in a true golfer's paradise overlooking the second fairway with a serene waterfront view. This expansive deck offers ample space for hosting endless outdoor gatherings, barbecues, and more. Whether savoring your morning coffee or enjoying a sunset cocktail, this outdoor oasis provides the perfect setting for both relaxation and entertainment.
